fields.description: Meet. The first chip designed specifically for the Mac. The Apple M1 chip brings unique technologies to your Mac and delivers incredible performance combined with industry-leading power efficiency. This is not just another step for the Mac - this is a whole new level of possibilities.

fields.name: Canon EOS20000
fields.description:
Ideal as your first DSLR: Intuitive controls for capturing and sharing beautiful shots with blurry backgrounds.
Unleash your creativity and save memorable moments easily.

fields.description: Image quality is the most important aspect of working with multimedia content, and the exclusive True Pixel display boasts the excellent performance required for this. 4K resolution, wide color coverage (100% Adobe RGB), accurate color transfer (Delta-E <2), True Color technology and CalMan certification - this display will be an ideal tool for design or video editing.

fields.description:
